# ðŸ›¡ï¸ Fortinet Cybersecurity Training & Accreditation Roadmap

This roadmap provides a modular guide to Fortinetâ€™s certification ecosystem, focused on cybersecurity roles and governance-aligned delivery. It reflects the updated Network Security Expert (NSE) framework as of October 2023.

